name: the allergy
description: The consequence of having become accustomed to the air without oxygen (to the black smoke that fills the alveoli of those who walk around hoping that life will bring them something better or that the miraculous luck of some event will solve their problems overnight) had caused in them a profound rejection or rather, an itching and unstoppable allergy to the pure air of a city polluted by cold springs, by true lies and a lot of appearances, rather, a spicy and unstoppable allergy to the pure air of a city polluted by cold springs, by true lies and a lot of appearances that made the suicide of young people who were lost between what they wanted to have and what they did not see they had.
